name: A Greedy Goblin
description: A Pact between Collector and Creator. Whomever holds this objkt, may trade it at anytime for a non reserved 5/5 (or more) object that the creator holds free of charge. Likely done just before the minting of a new objkt by the creator, should the holder desire to activate "A Greedy Goblin" DM the creator and send "A Greedy Goblin" back to the creator's wallet. The holder may also sell this objkt if they so desire.
